"{\"uid\": \"rappler.com-sports-updates-results-highlights-team-philippines-paris-olympics-july-27-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  SUMMARY  This is AI generated summarization, which may have errors.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 69, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9189899360848929, \"rank\": 0.0881505485042745, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For context, always refer to the full article.\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MANILA, Philippines - Team Philippines kicks off its Paris Olympics campaign on Saturday, July 27, as gymnastCarlos Yuloand rowerJoanie Delgacoopen their respective bids.\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9996903755009077, \"rank\": 0.00030968679778980643, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 145, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9996903755009077, \"rank\": 0.00030968679778980643, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 171, \"end\": 185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carlos Yulo gets three medal chances as he advances to the individual all-around, floor exercise, and vault finals following the conclusion of the men's artistic gymnastics qualification.\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 290, \"end\": 301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo placed second in floor exercise with 14.766 points, sixth in vault with an average of 14.683 points, and ninth in the all-around with a total of 83.631 points.\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the other apparatuses, Yulo ranked 19th in parallel bars, 27th in horizontal bar, 40th in pommel horse, and 49th in still rings.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9311661138021114e-41, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Full storyhere.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 793, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carlos Yulo is on track to advance to the men's all-around final as he ranks eighth through two of the three qualification subdivisions with a total of 83.631 points.\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 795, \"end\": 806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The top 24 - with a maximum of two per country - will reach the all-around final.\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1044, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also hopes to reach two apparatus finals as he sits at second in floor exercise and sixth in vault, with the top eight (maximum of two per country) qualifying for the medal round.\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carlos Yulo tallies a respectable 13.466 points in horizontal bar to wrap up the men's all-around qualification.\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1342, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1230, \"end\": 1241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carlos Yulo displays consistency in one of his pet events as he scores 14.533 in parallel bars.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1344, \"end\": 1355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo improves on the 13.466 points he scored in the same apparatus in the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carlos Yulo amasses 14.8 and 14.566 points in his two vaults as he propels himself into contention for a spot in the finals.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1529, \"end\": 1540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With an average of 14.683 points, Yulo currently ranks fourth in the apparatus behind Great Britain's Harry Hepworth (14.766), Croatia's Aurel Benovic (14.733), and Great Britain's Jake Jarman (14.699).\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1689, \"end\": 1693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9311661138021114e-41, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}, {\"begin\": 1741, \"end\": 1754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9750654389898434, \"rank\": 0.025568856604267557, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1763, \"end\": 1771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Hepworth\", \"score\": 0.9999999999913598, \"rank\": 8.625967690065075e-12, \"text\": \"Hepworth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Hepworth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Hepworth\"}, {\"begin\": 1782, \"end\": 1789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999052036474582, \"rank\": 8.893077651706411e-05, \"text\": \"Croatia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1820, \"end\": 1833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9750654389898434, \"rank\": 0.025568856604267557, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1836, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"score\": 0.9715430336092916, \"rank\": 0.028831580776493195, \"text\": \"Jake\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the Tokyo Olympics, Yulo reached the vault final and narrowly missed a medal as he finished fourth.\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1961, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carlos Yulo misses the cut for the final of still rings after garnering 13.0 points in the men's all-around qualification.\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 2085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1963, \"end\": 1974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He finished with 14.0 points in the same apparatus in the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2157, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carlos Yulo earns 13.066 points in pommel horse in the men's all-around qualification.\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2159, \"end\": 2170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That means he will miss the final of the apparatus, with only the top eight - a maximum of two per country - advancing.\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2366, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, his score is a major improvement to the 11.833 points he recorded in pommel horse in the Tokyo Games as Yulo aims to make the all-around final.\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carlos Yulo lets out a loud roar, seemingly satisfied after a stellar floor exercise performance in the men's all-around qualification.\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2655, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2520, \"end\": 2531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He nets 14.766 points to put himself in prime position of making the top eight and reaching the final.\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2759, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Currently, only Great Britain's Jake Jarman has a better score with 14.966 points, while defending champion Artem Dolgopyat is behind with 14.466 points.\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2777, \"end\": 2790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9750654389898434, \"rank\": 0.025568856604267557, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2793, \"end\": 2797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"score\": 0.9715430336092916, \"rank\": 0.028831580776493195, \"text\": \"Jake\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\"}, {\"begin\": 2869, \"end\": 2884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artem_Dolgopyat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Artem Dolgopyat\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artem_Dolgopyat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artem_Dolgopyat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Joanie Delgaco missed out on an outright quarterfinal berth in the women's single sculls after placing fourth in Heat 2.\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 3036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2916, \"end\": 2922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joanie_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.7635785748135286, \"rank\": 0.30962291633714484, \"text\": \"Joanie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joanie_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joanie_Cunningham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Delgaco clocked 7:56.26 to finish behind the Netherlands' Karolien Florijin (7:36.90), Switzerland's Aurelia-Maxima Katharina Janzen (7:41.15), and Slovenia's Nina Kostanjsek (7:46.30).\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3083, \"end\": 3094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6003251997870718, \"rank\": 0.6594572200150834, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3125, \"end\": 3136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9880098410906573, \"rank\": 0.004722591456772354, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3164, \"end\": 3170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_H._Janzen\", \"score\": 0.9999985847667641, \"rank\": 1.3570460650831706e-06, \"text\": \"Janzen\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_H._Janzen\", \"d